           TestCase "C-13 Mock of call with a new call as exception handling ending with period works"
           MOCK CALL 'PROGRAM' USING VALUE-1
                MOVE "worked" TO VALUE-1
           END-MOCK
           MOCK CALL 'PROGRAM2' USING VALUE-1
                MOVE "notworked" TO VALUE-1
